{"type": "article", "id": 20422, "title": "Super 8 film camera", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-08T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122332ntHqDAQ1moEKYfpM.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在消费电子展（CES 2016）上，柯达联合硅谷设计师 Yves Behar 重新推出了 Super 8 film camera，它是 1965 年推出的经典款。新版依然采用胶片拍摄，滑开侧面菱形的开仓可以放入录影带，此外设置了 USB、耳机接口，数字取景器，SD 卡槽，适应数码时代。Yves Behar 设计的外观显得棱角分明，镜头是突出来的，类似一个酒壶。它有多种颜色可选，目前还没有上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122329ZwgUA5kTyVehN4om.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67948718\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122330iG0D6kBbA39QZY2y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122330HK61VWZu94X5BAT0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8707265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122331T547p39FvAR6byG2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60042735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}